705998f-a.title: Brooklyn: New Jersey Avenue - Glenmore Avenue
705998f-a.text:
New Jersey Avenue, east side, north from Glenmore Avenue, show-
ing the St. Johannes Evangelical Lutheran Church. This edifice re-
placed the old wooden church, which stood on the corner of Liberty
Avenue.
September 14, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
